high_descs: Leave the room. Turn right. Enter the room. Turn left. Continue to the coffeetable. Turn right until you are in front of the coffeetable.
Exit the room. Go straight ahead and when you reach a shelf on the left, turn right. Reach the sink and turn right.
Place the knife on the left side of the sink. Open the faucet for 4 seconds. Turn the faucet off. Take the knife.
Return to the room. Stand in front of the sidetable.
Place the knife on the right side of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Find a knife, grind it and place it on a side table.

high_descs: Turn right and head right to reach the room at the end of the passage and turn left to reach the coffee table.
Pick up the knife from the coffee table.
Turn right and head right to walk down the passage and turn right to reach the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink and take it out.
Turn right to exit the kitchen and turn left and head right to reach the side table in the bedroom.
Put the knife on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed knife on the side table.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffee table
Take the knife from the coffee table
Turn around and go near the sink
Put the knife into the sink and washed it
Turn around and go near the side table
Put the knife on the side table
anns.task_desc: Placed the knife on the side table
